{"tid":1865502,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"組織工會唔係只係用黎罷工 係建立有動員能力既共同體","createTime":"2020-02-06T08:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T08:55:36.000Z","uid":126889,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6796c8388f79236529ff3fe3fe39874348a6f473","tid":1865502,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"就好似連登仔日日講既臨時政府咁<br />\n冇用或者只有單一面向 (eg. 象徵/ 罷工)<br />\n好快就好似馬鞍山商場咁冇哂聲氣<br />\n<br />\n所以係小弟眼中為罷工而成立工會只係幌子<br />\n最重要既事係組織到一班反賊去做唔同既事<br />\n<br />\n例如你係醫護 你有醫護界係資訊 人脈 同技術<br />\n組織左一班佔據左醫護界既人 建立自己既網絡 <br />\n先會知道唔依靠現有體制 而自己既網絡可以發揮到咩功能出黎<br />\n<br />\n工會聽講話有二萬人 手足既力量絕對唔止係罷工同總辭<br />\n好多野可以你地做左上面都吹你唔漲<br />\n好似黃色經濟圈咁 不如諗下一個屬於香港人既醫療網絡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adff6f6ea88838512e923be05b149f52f186aa09","tid":1865502,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"波蘭團結工會事件"},{"pid":"929d043a7b3f49c1a8ed8677df1aec42d17df93a","tid":1865502,"uid":192630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運輸海關醫護罷工救港<br />\n各行各業立即大罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433ad3c7c713275253bf4b67efd702673d69380f","tid":1865502,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b68a18f8868ea6f44c37a8c90a297f517f6350","tid":1865502,"uid":112355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8bad65783730b593e43b947cfcbd042b90d66d31","tid":1865502,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"其實組織工會唔應該用罷工黎做宣傳，應該重點講爭取應有勞工權益"},{"pid":"bf50e6d41e500977a336bb03b26321ee75985a5b","tid":1865502,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bad65783730b593e43b947cfcbd042b90d66d31","tid":1865502,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"其實組織工會唔應該用罷工黎做宣傳，應該重點講爭取應有勞工權益"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adc6badc4375db9d0224f29023e70c2550d6773","tid":1865502,"uid":265171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92a46ec294c3a47e00222ec138ff1d6f3303a57","tid":1865502,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"依我之見 辭職都唔應該<br />\n下下用自殺威脅 好快就唔會驚你<br />\n反之醫護可以不定期快閃罷工先玩到最盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e77502fa77505662aae316342a2765fe7f1721d","tid":1865502,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf50e6d41e500977a336bb03b26321ee75985a5b","tid":1865502,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bad65783730b593e43b947cfcbd042b90d66d31","tid":1865502,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"其實組織工會唔應該用罷工黎做宣傳，應該重點講爭取應有勞工權益"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"工聯會個d純粹係bribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要話比班人知有工會先唔會比人壓榨，要有應有權益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然都要有工聯會個種幫手搞下活動咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" 